org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.java.reverse.ui

Class ReverseSelectedNodeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.languages.java.reverse.ui.ReverseSelectedNodeVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IProjectExplorerNodeVisitor

    public class ReverseSelectedNodeVisitor
extends Object
implements IProjectExplorerNodeVisitor
    This visitor visit the provided Nodes. Node are usually selections from Eclipse Project/Package Explorers. This visitor walk the nodes and apply the appropriate code reverse.
    Author:
    cedric dumoulin
